811
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:46,350
Good stuff. Good stuff.

812
00:26:46,350 --> 00:26:47,680
Good stuff. Good stuff.

813
00:26:48,090 --> 00:26:49,050
Okay, thank you.

814
00:26:49,050 --> 00:26:49,590
