00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,760
Let's talk inside. Come.

1160
00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:31,760
Don't run! Don't run!

1161
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:33,740
The price is negotiable!

1162
00:36:33,920 --> 00:36:35,550
Seriously!

1163
00:36:35,650 --> 00:36:36,690
Give the money to her!

1164
00:36:36,690 --> 00:36:37,590
Give the money to her!

1165
00:36:37,590 --> 00:36:38,800
Good stuff!

1166
00:36:40,050 --> 00:36:40,980
This looks good.

1167
00:36:42,780 --> 00:36:44,460
Just use hand gestures.

1168
00:36:44,610 --> 00:36:45,260
Which one do you want?

1169
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:46,170
Are these jeans okay?

1170
00:36:46,170 --> 00:36:46,900
This one. Is it pretty?

1171
00:36:46,900 --> 00:36:47,420
This one.

1172
00:36:47,420 --> 00:36:48,620
It doesn't look good.

1173
00:36:48,820 --> 00:36:50,000
This old lady is quite picky.

1174
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:50,760
This one.

1175
00:36:50,780 --> 00:36:51,090
This one looks good.

1176
00:36:51,090 --> 00:36:52,130
Do you think they can take away

1177
00:36:52,130 --> 00:36:53,570
the money they earned here?

1178
00:36:53,570 --> 00:36:55,110
Of course not.

1179
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:56,040
Looks good!

1180
00:36:56,610 --> 00:36:58,570
Good stuff! Good stuff!

1181
00:36:58,590 --> 00:37:00,420
This much!

1182
00:37:00,590 --> 00:37:02,230
This much! For the whole set.

1183
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:04,110
Give the money to...

1184
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:05,090
to Zhuang Zhuang.

1185
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:05,950
Take the money!

1186
00:37:06,010 --> 00:37:07,410
This one looks good.

1187
00:37:07,500 --> 00:37:09,180
This one looks very good.

1188
00:37:33,570 --> 00:37:34,430
Zhuang Zhuang!

1189
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:36,850
Zhuang Zhuang!

1190
00:37:54,500 --> 00:37:55,210
Xu Shengli!

1191
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:57,900
What are you doing?

1192
00:37:59,590 --> 00:38:01,360
I am playing with snowballs.

1193
00:38:05,650 --> 00:38:07,710
I knocked on your door for a long time,

1194
00:38:07,780 --> 00:38:09,040
but you weren't there.

1195
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:10,940
So you're here having a snowball fight.

1196
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,260
I was wondering
why I kept throwing it at your window

1197
00:38:12,260 --> 00:38:13,820
and you didn't react.

1198
00:38:13,980 --> 00:38:15,500
Look whose room this is.

1199
00:38:16,980 --> 00:38:18,180
Isn't this your room?

1200
00:38:19,010 --> 00:38:21,490
Then... this is my room.

1201
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:23,340
Hurry up! Let's go!

1202
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:23,900
Let's go.

1203
00:38:23,940 --> 00:38:26,600
Liangliang... Liangliang is sleeping.
Hurry.

1204
00:38:35,980 --> 00:38:36,800
Who is it?

1205
00:38:37,190 --> 00:38:39,610
I didn't expect it
to go so smoothly this time.

1206
00:38:39,610 --> 00:38:40,300
Yeah.

1207
00:38:40,670 --> 00:38:41,870
It feels like a dream.

1208
00:39:07,670 --> 00:39:08,510
It sounds so good.

1209
00:39:08,510 --> 00:39:09,200
Thank you.

1210
00:39:27,190 --> 00:39:27,800
Bye-bye.

1211
00:39:31,380 --> 00:39:32,440
Careful, it's hot.

1212
00:39:32,820 --> 00:39:33,420
Thank you.

1213
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:37,680
I'll peel it for you.

1214
00:39:39,630 --> 00:39:40,690
Careful, it's hot.

1215
00:39:40,710 --> 00:39:41,620
It is a bit hot.

1216
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:42,520
It's fine.

1217
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:52,590
Okay.

1218
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:54,120
Hold the bottom.

1219
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:03,480
A whistle?

1220
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:05,820
It's for you.

1221
00:40:06,550 --> 00:40:07,900
I bought it at the train station.

1222
00:40:07,900 --> 00:40:09,510
Just think of it as a souvenir.

1223
00:40:09,510 --> 00:40:10,790
This is not a souvenir.

1224
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,380
It's an amulet.

1225
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:19,330
I get it.

1226
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,710
When I blow it,

1227
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:21,640
you will appear.

1228
00:40:23,130 --> 00:40:23,850
Maybe.

1229
00:40:30,460 --> 00:40:31,210
Alright.

1230
00:40:31,260 --> 00:40:32,500
I'm right here, aren't I?

1231
00:40:32,500 --> 00:40:33,750
I just want to blow it.

1232
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,900
Well... when I miss you...

1233
00:40:35,900 --> 00:40:36,830
I can blow it too.

1234
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:44,280
Look at your frozen ears.

1235
00:40:45,150 --> 00:40:47,280
You didn't wear a hat when you went out.

1236
00:40:49,130 --> 00:40:50,690
What did you say?

1237
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:55,730
I said,

1238
00:40:57,650 --> 00:40:59,280
I found that I quite like you.

1239
00:41:04,820 --> 00:41:06,820
I didn't hear what you said clearly.

1240
00:41:09,960 --> 00:41:11,260
I said the blood supply to your brain

1241
00:41:11,260 --> 00:41:12,150
comes and goes.

1242
00:41:13,630 --> 00:41:15,430
Didn't you say you quite like me?

1243
00:41:30,300 --> 00:41:31,460
You don't know

1244
00:41:31,460 --> 00:41:32,760
how happy I am.

1245
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:33,710
Just these past few days,

1246
00:41:33,710 --> 00:41:34,360
I've brought in so many people

1247
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:35,690
that we could form a whole company.

1248
00:41:35,690 --> 00:41:36,980
So it has nothing to do with me?

1249
00:41:36,980 --> 00:41:37,890
It does.

1250
00:41:37,980 --> 00:41:39,200
Just a little bit.

1251
00:41:39,300 --> 00:41:40,510
I really didn't expect

1252
00:41:40,510 --> 00:41:41,230
that besides me,

1253
00:41:41,230 --> 00:41:42,420
Liangliang is also

1254
00:41:42,420 --> 00:41:43,940
quite popular in Russia, right?

1255
00:41:43,940 --> 00:41:44,300
Jun,

1256
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:44,920
our goods

1257
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:45,880
are almost sold out.

1258
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:46,880
What do we do next?

1259
00:41:47,780 --> 00:41:49,460
I wanted to tell you guys earlier

1260
00:41:49,460 --> 00:41:50,720
that the cost

1261
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,710
of restocking and exchanging goods locally

1262
00:41:52,710 --> 00:41:53,440
was too high.

1263
00:41:54,190 --> 00:41:54,980
I heard

1264
00:41:55,190 --> 00:41:56,110
that in Vladivostek,

1265
00:41:56,110 --> 00:41:56,860
they just got a batch

1266
00:41:56,860 --> 00:41:57,800
of bulk clothing from China.

1267
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:58,710
It's Vladivostok.

1268
00:41:58,710 --> 00:41:59,590
That's not important.

1269
00:41:59,590 --> 00:42:00,650
You know what I mean.

1270
00:42:00,650 --> 00:42:01,440
They got a batch

1271
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:02,650
of bulk Chinese clothing,

1272
00:42:02,650 --> 00:42:03,920
and the quality is excellent.

1273
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,210
But I didn't dare to take the offer.

1274
00:42:05,210 --> 00:42:05,710
Why?

1275
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:07,150
Because our sales volume wasn't that high,

1276
00:42:07,150 --> 00:42:07,840
and we didn't have

1277
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:08,900
that much capital.

1278
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:09,580
But now that

1279
00:42:09,710 --> 00:42:11,650
our sales
have gone up these past two days.

1280
00:42:11,650 --> 00:42:12,170
Right?

1281
00:42:12,260 --> 00:42:13,130
I calculated our earnings,

1282
00:42:13,130 --> 00:42:14,260
and we have enough capital now.

1283
00:42:14,260 --> 00:42:16,280
So I took the liberty

1284
00:42:17,550 --> 00:42:18,900
of calling them today.

1285
00:42:20,230 --> 00:42:22,130
I think we have a great chance

1286
00:42:22,440 --> 00:42:23,440
to make big money.

1287
00:42:25,010 --> 00:42:28,150
Mr. Lucky deserves his name.

1288
00:42:29,050 --> 00:42:30,670
Find Mr. Lucky and be lucky!

1289
00:42:30,670 --> 00:42:31,050
Right?

1290
00:42:31,050 --> 00:42:31,630
175,000.

1291
00:42:31,670 --> 00:42:31,960
Okay.

1292
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:33,160
Come on, let's drink.

1293
00:42:35,650 --> 00:42:36,110
I'll go.

1294
00:42:38,500 --> 00:42:39,760
Sophia is back, right?

1295
00:42:41,030 --> 00:42:41,510
Hello.

1296
00:42:42,150 --> 00:42:42,820
Hello.

1297
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:44,070
I am the one

1298
00:42:44,070 --> 00:42:46,590
selling goods at the market lately.

1299
00:42:47,050 --> 00:42:47,960
We're in the same business,

1300
00:42:47,960 --> 00:42:49,190
and we're also compatriots.

1301
00:42:49,190 --> 00:42:49,820
I'm Chinese.

1302
00:42:49,820 --> 00:42:50,570
Hello.

1303
00:42:50,630 --> 00:42:51,460
My surname is Du.

1304
00:42:51,460 --> 00:42:52,440
Just call me Du.

1305
00:42:53,550 --> 00:42:54,790
Can I help you?
